title: Villa for Rent $3550 3 beds, 2 baths, 2 car garage
posting_body: ["Here's your opportunity to live in the award-winning community of ARDEN.", 'This Gorgeous (Sydney Model) Villa, 3BR/2BA and enclosed Office or Den includes the following', '- Newly built (Oct 2021), open concept floor plan - 1,836sqft A/C (2,386sqft - total)', '- Tiles all through out the home, hurricane and storm rated windows and glass sliding patio doors', "- Spacious master on-suite (13'x17') with 2 separate walk-in closets, his/her sink and stand-up shower", "- 2 bedrooms (12'6''x12') and (10'8''x12'4'') with ample natural light", '- Flex room is enclosed with modern glass French doors, perfect for office space or den', '- Gorgeous quartz counter tops in Kitchen, Kitchen island and bathrooms', '- Brand new appliances - washer and dryer, refrigerator, microwave and gas stove', '- 2 car garage comes with beautiful built-in cabinets and overhead storage, perfect for storing beach gear', '- garage also comes with brand new Kenmore upright freezer, perfect for holding extra groceries', "- home comes with preinstalled TV mounts in living room (can hold up to 82'' TV), master bedroom (can hold up to 65'' TV) and in office / den (can hold up to 46'' TV)", '- beautiful covered patio and covered porch area', '- great size backyard with zero lawn maintenance for you to enjoy peacefully', 'Arden amenities include', '- 20 miles of trails, lakes, fitness center, tennis courts, boat launch ramp, Soccer field, Basketball and Volleyball Court', '- Resort Style Pools and Clubhouse', '- Golf cart and pet friendly community', 'Schools are Wellington A Rated schools.']
